      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n  - The applicant must be a farmer.\n  - The applicant must be a resident of Gujarat.\n  - The applicant must have a minimum land between 0.20 ha and 1 ha.\n  - The applicant must procure quality planting materials from a nursery and start the plantation.\n\n&gt; **Note:** Preference will be given to small-scale and women farmers.\n\n",
